  "Description": {
    "English": "A three-variety pack of assorted fireworks, containing <span class=\"name name-commodity\">luxury</span>, <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Atlas</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">fleshy</span> variations. Ignite to create fascinating displays in the sky.<br><br>Place launch tube via the <VAL_ON>Build Menu<> (<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>). <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Warning</span>: Aim away from living creatures. Not recommended for indoor use.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一包包含三种烟花的综合烟花包。其中包含<span class=\"name name-commodity\">奢华</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">阿特拉斯</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">血肉</span>烟花。点燃就可以在天空中开启一场不可思议的光影表演。<br><br>可以通过<VAL_ON>建造菜单<>（<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>）来放置发射筒。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：不可瞄准活体生物。不建议在室内使用。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "三種綜合煙火的組合包，包含<span class=\"name name-commodity\">豪華</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">寰宇</span>與<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">血肉</span>煙火。點燃即可在天空中創造出迷人效果。<br><br>可從<VAL_ON>建造選單<> (<span class=\"name name-img\">BUILD_MENU</span>) 放置發射管。<span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：請勿對著生物發射，不建議於室內使用。"
  },
